    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把三个子图画出来：DEV里面放Commit/PR节点，CI子图里放Build、Test、Deploy三个节点，ENV里放Service Live。方向用从左到右。",
